{"tid":2356382,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"科大新宿舍2023年落成 容納1500人","createTime":"2021-01-06T19:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:30:00.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d7633c6e64aca64581a91d2d144000e43e113506","tid":2356382,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:02:59.000Z","msg":"ZHA and L&amp;O have unveiled a new design for the Student Residence Development at the Hong Kong University of Science and Technology, one of the leading research institutions in Asia and around the world. Created after an urgent demand for new residential facilities and halls within the campus, the project is scheduled for completion in 2023.<br />\n<br />\nDesigned by Zaha Hadid Architects in collaboration with Leigh &amp; Orange, the newest additions to the Hong Kong University of Science and Technology will house over 1,500 students. Inspired by the university&rsquo;s mission &ldquo;to harness technology and innovation to solve today&rsquo;s critical global issues&rdquo;, the project combines advanced digital design technologies with sustainable construction practices and operational strategies."},{"pid":"ad33ee63768dc8c888295b9911902ce5bcee8584","tid":2356382,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.adsttc.com/media/images/5ff4/463e/63c0/17cd/f900/03af/medium_jpg/04_ZHA_HKUST_Roofline_Render_by_Visual_Brick.jpg?1609844236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.adsttc.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5ff4%2F463e%2F63c0%2F17cd%2Ff900%2F03af%2Fmedium_jpg%2F04_ZHA_HKUST_Roofline_Render_by_Visual_Brick.jpg%3F1609844236&h=1a52a623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.adsttc.com/media/images/5ff4/4822/63c0/1725/9000/043b/medium_jpg/06_ZHA_HKUST_V_Node_Communal_Render_by_Visual_Brick.jpg?1609844746\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.adsttc.co